DQMSampleData_SQL.@EndUserText.label: DQMSampleData_SQL
DQMSampleData_SQL.@DataWarehouse.sqlEditor.query:
SELECT "ID","STD_ADDR_COUNTRY_3CHAR","STD_ADDR_COUNTRY_NAME","ADDR_ASMT_INFO", "ADDR_ASMT_LEVEL", "ADDR_INFO_CODE",
"ADDR_INFO_CODE_MSG", "GEO_ASMT_LEVEL",
(CASE 
  WHEN "ADDR_ASMT_INFO" = 'V' OR "ADDR_ASMT_INFO" = 'C' THEN 'Valid' 
  ELSE 'Invalid' END) AS "Address_Validity",
(CASE 
  WHEN "ADDR_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'S' OR "ADDR_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'PR' THEN 'Premise'
  WHEN "ADDR_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'PN' THEN 'Street'
  WHEN "ADDR_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'L4' OR "ADDR_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'L3' OR "ADDR_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'L2' OR "ADDR_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'L1' THEN 'City'
  WHEN "ADDR_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'R' OR "ADDR_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'C' THEN 'Region'
  ELSE 'Unassigned' END) AS "Address_Level",
(CASE WHEN "GEO_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'PRE' OR "GEO_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'PRI' THEN 'Premise'
  WHEN "GEO_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'PN' THEN 'Street'
  WHEN "GEO_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'PF' OR "GEO_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'P2P' OR "GEO_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'P1' THEN 'Postcode'
  WHEN "GEO_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'L3' OR "GEO_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'L2' OR "GEO_ASMT_LEVEL" = 'L1' THEN 'City'
  ELSE 'Unassigned' END) AS "Geocode_Level"
FROM "DQMSampleData"
